'''Baruur''' ({{lang-en|lipid}}; {{lang-ar|دهنيات}}) waa koox iskudhisyo dabiici ah kuwaasi oo u samaysan [[malakuyuul]]o ay ka mid yihiin [[dux]]d, [[xaydh]]a, [[fiitamiin|fiitamiinada milma]] (sida Fiitamiin A, D, E, iyo K) iyo walxo kale oo badan oo si dabiici ah looga helo jidhka [[dad]]ka, [[xayawaan]]ka iyo in badan oo [[dhir]]ta ka mid ah.<ref> Lipids have applications in the cosmetic and food industries as well as in nanotechnology.</ref> Sidoo kale, noocyo badan oo baruurta ahi waa [[iskudhis]] ka mid sadexda nooc ee [[nafaqo]]da [[jidh]]ka [[dad]]ka, [[xayawaan]]ka, [[dhir]]ta iyo guud ahaan [[noole|nooluhu]] u baahan yahay; labada kale waa [[borotiin]] iyo [[karbohydrate]].<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.mckinley.illinois.edu/handouts/macronutrients.htm|title = Macronutrients: the Importance of Carbohydrate, Protein, and Fat|date = |accessdate = 20 September 2014|website = McKinley Health Center|publisher = [[University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign]]}}</ref>  

Duxda oo [[Saynis]] ahaan loo yaqaano ''triglycerides'' waxay ka kooban tahay iskudhisyo silsilad asiid-baruur ah, alkohol iyo glycerol. Sida caadiga ah duxda waxaa laga helaa [[saliid]]a, [[subag]]a iyo [[baruur]]ta [[xoolo|xoolaha]] iyo [[xayawaan]]ka. Sidoo kale waxaa jira noocyo ka mid ah [[dhir]]ta oo leh dux waloow ay tahay nooc ka duwan tan xoolaha iyo xayawaanka.

Intaas waxaa dheer, duxdu kuma milanto [[biyo|biyaha]] iyo noocyo kale oo [[dareere]]ha ka mid ah (sida [[caano|caanaha]]).<ref>United Kingdom [http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/1996/1499/contents/made The Food Labelling Regulations 1996] &ndash; [http://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/1996/1499/schedule/7/made Schedule 7: Nutrition labelling]</ref>

